Former Lebanese Prime Minister Rafik Hariri was killed in a powerful explosion in central Beirut on Monday , Lebanese officials and medical sources said .It said Hariri was targeted because `` he was an agent '' for Saudi Arabia .He was Rafik Hariri , a former and a future prime minister of Lebanon .But Hariri 's supporters have accused Syria and the Lebanese government of orchestrating the assassination .At least eight others were also killed , including some of Hariri 's bodyguards .Hariri was important as a symbol of Lebanon to the outside world .